* rc.sp
* David_Harris@hmc.edu 2/2/03
* Find the response of RC circuit to rising input
*--------------------------------------------------------------
* Parameters and models
*--------------------------------------------------------------
.option post
*--------------------------------------------------------------
* Simulation netlist
*--------------------------------------------------------------
Vin in gnd pwl 0ps 0 100ps 0 150ps 1.0 1ns 1.0
R1 in out 2k
C1 out gnd 100f
*--------------------------------------------------------------
* Stimulus
*--------------------------------------------------------------
.tran 20ps 1ns
.plot v(in) v(out)
.end
